summary: AN ORDINANCE accepting electrical overhead and underground distribution easements over portions of Thormod's Addition; southeast quarter of Section 22, Township 23 North, Range 4 East; southeast quarter of Section 21, Township 26 North, Range 4 East; vacated Arroyo Beach Place S.W.; Adams Home Tracts First Addition; southwest 1/4 of Section 21, Township 25 North, Range 4 East, and Lake Forest Park Estates.
